room_title: Escape room "Telegraph" by Alley Escape at Regal Lanes in Detroit
room_description: Welcome to the untouchables. Elliott Ness has hired you to help him bring down the biggest gangster of them all - the infamous Al Capone. We have a warrant to search one of his private speakeasies and we have reason to believe his ledger is hidden in there somewhere. You have exactly one hour to either find it and put him away for good... or be on the hit list of the most dangerous man alive!
